1265
01:07:55,154 --> 01:07:57,989
Yeah, but you... You let him go.

1266
01:07:58,407 --> 01:07:59,615
Didn't you?

1267
01:08:00,409 --> 01:08:03,202
A pretty French girl shows up out of the blue,
acts like she's my partner

1268
01:08:03,287 --> 01:08:04,996
- and then she lets the bad guy go?
- Let go of my arm.

1269
01:08:05,080 --> 01:08:06,748
Who exactly are you anyway?

1270
01:08:09,001 --> 01:08:11,002
I thought you said you were a desk agent.

1271
01:08:15,841 --> 01:08:17,091
Not bad.

1272
01:08:19,094 --> 01:08:20,094
What is this?

1273
01:08:23,140 --> 01:08:24,599
What's the Eye of Horus?

1274
01:08:24,808 --> 01:08:27,894
Oh, certainly nothing
I want to get into tonight.

1275
01:08:27,978 --> 01:08:30,521
