about me when you're sober.

1276
01:08:30,814 --> 01:08:32,690
Find your way back yourself.

1277
01:08:36,987 --> 01:08:40,198
Mr. Bradley? Mr. Tressler would like you
to join him for a drink.

1278
01:08:49,583 --> 01:08:50,625
Sir.

1279
01:08:50,834 --> 01:08:51,876
Thank you.

1280
01:08:53,462 --> 01:08:55,671
