1307
01:10:16,128 --> 01:10:17,712
No, you're not.

1308
01:11:38,627 --> 01:11:39,752
Hey.

1309
01:11:41,129 --> 01:11:43,297
I'm sorry for your arm.

1310
01:11:43,382 --> 01:11:44,966
No. I'm sorry.

1311
01:11:45,050 --> 01:11:47,301
I was an asshole. I was drunk.

1312
01:11:49,304 --> 01:11:51,889
