1329
01:12:48,238 --> 01:12:52,241
But it doesn't make any sense,
and I don't think logic will solve this for us.

1330
01:12:52,326 --> 01:12:54,910
- You don't say?
- No.

1331
01:12:56,288 --> 01:13:00,916
