Don't move!

1399
01:16:10,774 --> 01:16:12,691
Tell me.

1400
01:16:12,776 --> 01:16:14,360
Is my money being well-spent?

1401
01:16:15,028 --> 01:16:16,904
Exceedingly well.

1402
01:16:18,698 --> 01:16:20,199
Now you tell me,

1403
