All right, whoa, hold on, hold on!

1422
01:19:00,735 --> 01:19:02,569
- Really?
- Yup.

1423
01:19:06,741 --> 01:19:07,741
Oh, you...

1424
01:19:11,162 --> 01:19:12,621
You little...

