Shit!

1426
01:19:48,491 --> 01:19:49,533
Shit!

1427
01:19:50,952 --> 01:19:51,952
Give me that!

1428
01:20:18,188 --> 01:20:19,772
All units, cover the north exit now!

1429
01:20:19,856 --> 01:20:20,939
Clear on Evan.

1430
01:20:21,483 --> 01:20:23,025
Block every possible exit.

1431
01:20:23,151 --> 01:20:24,276
Hey! Get back... Shit.

1432
