1489
01:25:36,964 --> 01:25:38,965
who have been fast capturing
the public's imagination,

1490
01:25:39,050 --> 01:25:42,385
took a dark turn
when a police action that began in Chinatown

1491
01:25:42,470 --> 01:25:46,264
developed into a dramatic, high-speed chase
